    <body>
        <title>Encoding</title>
        <p>The <feature>encoding</feature> step is the final phase of the <feature>SPFE build</feature> process. It is responsible for creating the compiled deliverable, such as a PDF or EPub.</p>
        <p>The encoding step is not needed in all cases. If the final output is an XML or HTML format, no encoding is needed as the <feature>formatting</feature> step can create the final output directly.</p>
    </body>
